Collaborate with product owners to manage and prioritize the product backlog based on business value.
Track and communicate team velocity and sprint progress to stakeholders.
Foster a collaborative and transparent environment within the team and across departments.
Act as a servant leader and promote self-organization within the team.
Ensure adherence to Agile processes and encourage adoption of Agile best practices.
Support the adoption of Agile frameworks beyond Scrum where applicable.

